DESCRIPTION:• with Meghan Davis\n• Very competitive year: 6/98 funded.\n• R
 eview process:\n  1. Admin (Nov)\n  2. External reviewers (47 total)\, mix
  of academic\, industrial\,\n     pharma etc.\n  3. Each proposal had betw
 een 3-5 reviewers with written comments\n  4. Top 10-15% (so 10-15 because
  98 total) were discussed in a panel.\n     • Max score was 28\, cutoff fo
 r panel was 26.  *My proposal was\n       23.3*
